Report Highlights

How big is the area rugs market?

The global area rugs market size reached US$ 34.8 Billion in 2023. Looking forward, IMARC Group expects the market to reach US$ 54.2 Billion by 2032, exhibiting a growth rate (CAGR) of 4.9% during 2024-2032. 

What are area rugs?

Area rugs are an integral part of interior decor, offering both aesthetic appeal and practicality to homes and commercial spaces alike. These versatile floor coverings, typically smaller than carpets and often featuring intricate designs, serve various purposes, from adding warmth and texture to a room to defining specific areas within larger spaces. Area rugs come in an array of materials, patterns, and sizes to suit diverse preferences and needs in the world of interior design. Their popularity stems from their ability to effortlessly tie together different elements of a room, enhancing its overall ambiance and functionality.

